id":2131931,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T08:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9cee67676ab04bdbc6324214ef8f016ea6ab6ba","tid":2131931,"uid":176999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T08:18:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8c2a6677cb1297ea38907328eb904b91cc44119f","tid":2131931,"uid":282352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T08:18:25.000Z","msg":"手<span class=\"red\">炒</span>離職信<br />\n少油 唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e640ed3856b210b3c3615f8be10e124a1542c130","tid":2131931,"uid":132641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T08:19:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"37af9c0521a19503a753597167662764c594eaea","tid":2131931,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aee724335f3597e0c3e68a21ff7531dd544452e","tid":2131931,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T07:03:57.000Z","msg":"寶覺小學涉事教師莫德惠（莫Sir）向《蘋果》透露，本月被上門拘捕及控告後，該校校長鍾麗金即要求他手抄離職信，並須在信中訛稱在被捕前一天「自願」辭職。校方施壓期間，又涉禁止他致電律師，他引述鍾麗金當時稱「人權？你依家同我講人權？」校長否認有關指控，堅稱離職信是莫Sir自願書寫。有律師稱若指控屬實，校方涉嫌違偽造文書罪及刑事恐嚇。<br />\n<br />\n會面僵持一段時間後，莫Sir態度有所軟化，曾客氣詢問鍾能否讓他在寫信前，先致電律師徵詢意見，惟對方不允。他憶述當時情緒激動，強調致電律師是「基本人權」，惟鍾語帶嘲諷，「人權？你依家同我講人權？」他指警署尚且容許致電律師求助，但當天在學校比扣留在警署更難受。校長未待他開始動筆就離開會議室，他為求盡快離校，最終在其他教職員監視下，按草稿抄寫兩封親筆信。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200730/CWPHQKE5IKXMH55E47XHPBYA4I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2FCWPHQKE5IKXMH55E47XHPBYA4I%2F&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhJnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=f24f5a9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200730%2FCWPHQKE5IKXMH55E47XHPBYA4I%2F&h=a511d53d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200730/CWPHQKE5IKXMH55E47XHPBYA4I/</a>"},"cite